          <div class="pops">
            <h4>Guaranteed Authenticity</h4>

            <p>- All products have been hand checked by our quality control team to ensure their authenticity.</p>

            <p>- We use a 6 point checking process to ensure quality and authenticity.</p>

            <p>- Our authentication team have years of experience across hundreds of brands.</p>

            <p>- We guarantee your item to be 100% authentic or your money back.</p>

