              <a href="https://messinahembry.com/pages/quality-control"
                >Click here for full details of our authentication process.</a
              >
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pops-contain pop-2 pop-hide">
          <div class="pops">
            <h4>Sizing</h4>

            <p>
              - We understand that clothes sizing varies from brand, style and age which is why we hand measure all our
              items to ensure you know their true size.
            </p>

            <p>
              - Please always pay close attention to the measurements as these will give the best indication of a
              garments size.
            </p>

            <p>Measurement Guide:</p>

            <p>Pit to pit â€“ Taken from when the garment is laid flat from armpit to armpit.</p>

            <p>Pit to cuff â€“ Taken from the armpit to the end of the sleeve cuff.</p>

            <p>Length collar to hem â€“ Taken from the bottom of the collar to the hem of the garment.</p>

            <p>Waist â€“ Taken from the inside circumference.</p>

            <p>
              Leg Length â€“ Taken from the crotch seem to the bottom hem or from the top of the waist to the bottom hem
              on dresses and skirts.
            </p>

            <p>
              <a href="https://messinahembry.com/pages/sizing-guide">Please see our sizing page for further details</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pops-contain pop-3 pop-hide">
          <div class="pops">
            <h4>Delivery</h4>

            <p>Estimated delivery timeframes</p>

            <p>- UK standard deliveries 3-5 working days</p>

            <p>
              - UK Next Day Deliveres are dispatched the same day if ordered before 1pm. Next day deliveries exclude
              Saturdays.
            </p>

            <p>- Europe deliveries 5-12 working days</p>

            <p>- Worldwide deliveries 7-20 working days</p>

            <p>
              <a href="https://messinahembry.com/pages/delivery">Please see our postage page for further details</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pops-contain pop-4 pop-hide">
          <div class="pops">
            <h4>Returns</h4>

            <p>- All products come with our 30-day returns policy.</p>

            <p><a href="https://messinahembry.com/pages/returns">Please see our returns page for further details</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pops-contain pop-5 pop-hide">
          <div class="pops">
            <h4>Only One In Stock</h4>

            <p>All products are one off and unique.</p>

            <p>We only have one of each size and style in stock.</p>

            <p>
              Products don't hang about for very long and we can't reserve items so be sure to make your purchases as
              quickly as possible...
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if in_lightbox %}
        <div class="lightly-spaced-row-above">
          <a class="more" href="{{ product.url }}">
            {{ 'products.quick_buy.read_more' | t }}
            <span class="icon-small icon-natcol">{% include 'svg-chevron-right' %}</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      {% else %}
        {% if section.settings.show_sharing_icons %}
          <div class="desktop-only">
            {% include 'social-sharing',
              share_title: product.title,
              share_permalink: product.url,
              share_image: product
            %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% if section.settings.prod_desc_pos == 'below' and in_lightbox == false %}
      <div class="description user-content padded-row">{{ product.description }}</div>

      {% comment %} Add code to show under the description on the line below this one, if full-width underneath the image {% endcomment %}
      <!-- Underneath the description -->
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  <!-- /.product-detail -->

  {% if in_lightbox == false %}
    <div class="mobile-only product-meta">
      {% if section.settings.prod_show_tags and product.tags.size > 0 %}
        <div class="tags tags-inline product-meta-row">
          <div class="container">
            <label>{{ 'products.product.tags' | t }}</label>
            <ul>
              {% for tag in product.tags %}
                <li>
                  <a href="{% if collection %}{{ collection.url }}{% else %}{{ routes.collections_url }}{% endif %}/{{ tag | handle }}">
                    {{- tag -}}
                  </a>
                </li>
              {% endfor %}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      {% if section.settings.show_sharing_icons %}
        <div class="product-meta-row">
          <div class="container">
            {% include 'social-sharing',
              share_title: product.title,
              share_permalink: product.url,
              share_image: product
            %}
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="product-meta-row further-nav">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="prev">
            {% if collection.previous_product %}
              <a
                class="control-prev"
                href="{{ collection.previous_product }}"
                aria-label="{{ 'products.product.previous' | t | escape }}"
              >
                {%- include 'svg-chevron-left' -%}
              </a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>

          <div class="see-more">
            {%- if section.settings.prod_show_type and product.type != blank -%}
              {%- assign product_type_handle = product.type | handle -%}
              {%- if collections[product_type_handle].handle == product_type_handle -%}
                {%- assign type_url = collections[product_type_handle].url -%}
              {%- else -%}
                {%- assign type_url = product.type | url_for_type -%}
              {%- endif -%}
              {{ product.type | link_to: type_url }}
            {% endif %}
          </div>

          <div class="next">
            {% if collection.next_product %}
              <a
                class="control-next"
                href="{{ collection.next_product }}"
                aria-label="{{ 'products.product.next' | t | escape }}"
              >
                {%- include 'svg-chevron-right' -%}
              </a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

